channel.title: "Worst" project swap - shine up your not great projects here!
channel.description: If you have made some worst projects then come to me I can improve any projects you want me to make. Like for some kind of a long freakin example today I saw someone trying to recreate Yummy by Justin Bieber and I saw the project it just needs some touch to the song (here’s from before: https://app.auxy.co/projects/DZaphMq2jZr_7sxjDnygbg== sounds bad right? Just being honest okay?) so after I improved everything I almost thought that people will give more love to me but no. I’m giving all of my love to the person that recreated Yummy. So I wanted to improve all of your worst projects. If you have some bad ones give me the project link and then after 25 to 45 minutes it’s finally improved and finished and then your friends,your family,your school EVERYONE WILL LOVE IT. (So here’s after https://app.auxy.co/projects/cZUp6rRp2sOSffeYtW__gA== oh stop your making me blush so hard) so please if you have a bad project just come here and let me improve. Thanks so much for listening and I hope you have a blessed and amazing time. Peace & May Allah Bless you all!!! (P.S:if you red this message screenshot it to remember this. Thanks you.)
